{"hc52edb4bg6424g4165ga745gb847d15b4856": ["So, here we are. Surrounded by filth.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "bcabe7a9-27da-9540-9d5f-1fec3b177f87"], "hf072cf86g6d99g4506g8454g4513b885cdf2": ["Tell me you had a plan beyond 'put us in danger'?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "b7f3618d-a72c-8a64-b754-b3f8e2d530c6"], "h6b2314a9gd3f1g450agbdbegb2810e0c9f80": ["Of course. We fight!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "ed0987f9-c305-eee0-5a60-69d5fd362479"], "h1d802a94g7aacg4825g9eb2g0dbfbbd066d7": ["'Put us in danger' it is, then.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "0b764114-26f5-e1c3-db79-c596db91f671"], "h158ec846g24ecg4003gb0fbgb661d52dd5fa": ["Let's at least see what's happening first? You can commit suicide after that.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "bc9e73d1-0af2-3314-763b-659737a1d5f3"], "hc32bff19g4e2eg44adgb494ge1e10246e529": ["Let's mingle - find out what they know.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "d125bf01-f118-d44a-091c-ba257918b2d1"], "h1f7f22e2gd1f6g44a4gad36gd42350cad73f": ["A well-dressed elf and ... you. Yes, I'm sure we'll blend right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "h6ec204d3g1872g44abg9c8bg15e0ecb0236e": ["Yes, an elf and a traveller from another plane. I'm sure we'll fit right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "hf19b01b1g1adcg4be6g8dcdgebc14c19a0bd": ["An elf and a tiefling? Yes, I'm sure we'll blend right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "hba76bd3fgfd0fg4e84g8b61g050d4c68b070": ["An elf and a githyanki? Yes, I'm sure we'll blend right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "h08f76e9bg64d8g46b6gbf46gf72748b42a83": ["An elf and a miniature dragon? Yes, I'm sure we'll blend right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "h7c790dcag3c41g4f3fg9755gde3025ae992c": ["Yes. Yes, I'm sure we'll blend right in.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "7c4543bd-daf5-c1cb-f3a9-335b22adac69"], "h00353ffag5896g4538g9c21g03bfd8b32821": ["We keep our distance, maintain a low profile, and scout the camp.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "6e30e7c4-baea-2392-d041-0b6c06e970d7"], "h4bcf1c69g34ffg457cga0f0g7267b03341b1": ["Easy for you to say - you blend right in with this crowd.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "3da96f5a-441f-61e7-9535-b9f7ee2be481"], "hf1e6a59ag2c88g4dabg8ce8g2cc46b445a6d": ["Easy for you to say, I'm twice the size of these runts.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "3da96f5a-441f-61e7-9535-b9f7ee2be481"], "ha8ccc6aeg2e0fg45d4g9492gafbbc47db867": ["A low profile? I'm twice as tall as these runts.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "3da96f5a-441f-61e7-9535-b9f7ee2be481"], "h9f17b865ga991g4430g8112g7e7b09f8006d": ["... Yes.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "21c49437-9e20-2369-596f-54712d7a4f44"], "h7ae2c636g8fd6g438agaa99gbbac5eb5d7eb": ["Unbelievable.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "de54d024-0813-be82-cac2-295a56364d1a"], "h03383947gc862g4aedg8288g27bf392b300a": ["Let's just get this over with. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GOB_Checkpoint_RD_GoblinCampSneakIntro_Astarion.html", "d7a2f632-549f-93b9-a43a-f8c4844a7f0c"]}